    "description": "Cafe Coffee Day is actively seeking a talented and motivated Department Manager to join our dynamic team in Ahmedabad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Cafe Coffee Day:\nCafe Coffee Day is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cafe Coffee Day!",
